-- Lachlan Murdoch Set to Complete Purchase of Ten Stake, Review Reports
-- B y   W e n d y   P u g h
-- 2010-11-16T20:13:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/lachlan-murdoch-set-to-complete-purchase-of-ten-stake-review-reports.html
Lachlan Murdoch is expected to
complete the purchase of a stake in Ten Network Holdings Ltd.
from James Packer in about a week, the Australian Financial
Review reported, citing industry sources. Murdoch has secured
financing for the purchase, which will cost at least A$130
million, with the deal to be completed at least two weeks before
he joins the company board, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Pugh in Melbourne at 
